lead_paragraph: Poland's Agnieszka Radwanska stayed patient in the face of a barrage of big serving to advance to the last four of the WTA Finals for the third time in a row with a 7-5 6-3 victory over Karolina Pliskova on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Radwanska Stands Firm to Reach Singapore Semis
headline.main: Radwanska Stands Firm to Reach Singapore Semis
